1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Bb4+ 4. Bd2 Qe7 5. a3 Bxd2+ 6. Nbxd2 {White wants to
speed up his development and the occupation of the centre with e2-e4.} d6 7. e4
(7. e3 {is less consistent.} O-O 8. Be2 (8. Bd3 e5 {exposes the bishop.} 9. Qc2
Re8 10. dxe5 dxe5 11. Ng5 h6 12. Nge4 Nxe4 13. Bxe4 Nd7 14. O-O Nc5 15. Bd5 c6
16. Bf3 e4 17. Be2 Bf5 18. b4 Nd3 $11 {Ibrahimli,M (2379) -Bekturov,T (2297)
Porto Carras 2018 (1/2-1/2, 44)}) 8... e5 9. dxe5 (9. d5 {offers White a
passive version of the blocked structure.} a5 10. b4 Ne8 11. O-O f5 12. Nb3
axb4 13. axb4 Rxa1 14. Qxa1 Nf6 $11 {1/2-1/2 Kratochvil,M (2119) -Inneman,M 
