Ng5 Nc5 17. b4 Bd7 18. Qxa8 Rxa8 19. bxc5 e3 $15) 14... Bxf3 15. exf3 Rxb2 {
, with excellent play.}) 9... e5 10. d5 Nb8 11. b4 {A natural attempt to take
